Fixing some typos / links

Correct Images: Layered filesystems link.

The link was to `public/images.md` and should be `public/docker-images.md`.

Remove LXC as a substitute for linux containers

Refer to Linux Containers as cgroups and namepsaces.  LXC is a specific user land library for modifying cgroups and namespaces, but is not the default implementation used by Docker.
